Metadata-Version: 2.4
Name: study-task-tracker
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: FastAPI prototype for a study task tracker with quality gates (tests, lint, type-checking).
Author: Karina Shakhdullaeva
Requires-Python: >=3.11
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
Requires-Dist: fastapi>=0.115.0
Requires-Dist: uvicorn[standard]>=0.29.0
Requires-Dist: pydantic>=2.6.0
Provides-Extra: dev
Requires-Dist: pytest>=8.0.0; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: pytest-cov>=4.1.0; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: allure-pytest>=2.13.5; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: httpx>=0.27.0; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: black>=24.10.0; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: isort>=5.13.2; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: ruff>=0.6.5; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: mypy>=1.11.2; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: pre-commit>=4.0.1; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: types-requests; extra == "dev"
Requires-Dist: types-python-dateutil; extra == "dev"



## Установка

```bash
python -m venv .venv
. .venv/Scripts/activate  # Windows PowerShell: .\.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -U pip
pip install -e .[dev]
```

## Тесты и покрытие

```bash
pytest
```
Порог покрытия: >= 90%.

## Allure

```bash
pytest --alluredir=allure-results
allure serve allure-results
```

## Линтеры/форматирование/типы

```bash
ruff check .
black .
isort .
mypy .
```

## pre-commit

```bash
pre-commit install --hook-type pre-commit --hook-type pre-push
```

## Запуск приложения

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Структура

```
app/
  api/
  domain/
  dto/
  repositories/
  services/
  main.py
tests/
docs/
```
